@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Home Page";
    Layout = "~/Views/Shared/_Layout.cshtml";
}

<div id="carouselExampleIndicators" class="carousel slide mb-3" data-ride="carousel">
    <ol class="carousel-indicators">
        <li data-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-slide-to="0" class="active"></li>
        <li data-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-slide-to="1"></li>
        <li data-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-slide-to="2"></li>
    </ol>
    <div class="carousel-inner">
        <div class="carousel-item active">
            <img class="d-block w-100" src="./images/1.png" alt="First slide">
        </div>
        <div class="carousel-item">
            <img class="d-block w-100" src="./images/2.png" alt="Second slide">
        </div>
        <div class="carousel-item">
            <img class="d-block w-100" src="./images/3.png" alt="Third slide">
        </div>
    </div>
    <a class="carousel-control-prev" href="#carouselExampleIndicators" role="button" data-slide="prev">
        <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        <span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
    </a>
    <a class="carousel-control-next" href="#carouselExampleIndicators" role="button" data-slide="next">
        <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        <span class="sr-only">Next</span>
    </a>
</div>

<div class="row container mb-3">
    <div class="col-4 text-center">
        <h5 class="dashboard_header">INVESTMENT PLANNING</h5>
        <i class="faicon fa fa-line-chart fa-4x" aria-hidden="true"></i>
        <p class="text-justify">
            Starting proper investment planning begins with assessing your need for investment. We can help you understand how much money you must save in order to responsibly meet your commitments in life and accomplish your most important financial goals.
        </p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-4 text-center border-left">
        <h5 class="dashboard_header">FINANCIAL PLANNING</h5>
        <i class="faicon fa fa-inr fa-4x" aria-hidden="true"></i>
        <p class="text-justify">
            Managing wealth is a multifaceted topic that encompasses various areas of financial creation, preservation, and oversight. Our objective is to collaborate with you to design and implement personalized solutions and strategies that will help you accomplish your diverse financial goals.
        </p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-4 text-center border-left">
        <h5 class="dashboard_header">PRODUCT DELIVERY</h5>
        <i class="faicon fa fa-tachometer fa-4x" aria-hidden="true"></i>
        <p class="text-justify">
            The success of any plan or solution depends on its proper execution. As distributors of financial products, we provide you with access to a diverse selection of financial and non-financial products to enable effective implementation of your plans while taking into account your risk tolerance.
        </p>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="row">
    <div class="col-6 dashboardblock ">
        <h5 class="dashboard_header">ABOUT US</h5>
        <p class="text-justify">At, Royal Investments  our mission is to provide our clients with the best solutions in wealth creation and wealth management. We are driven to provide clients with simple, unbiased and uncluttered professional advice that adds value to their quality of life and results in actionable solutions.</p>

        <p class="text-justify">At, Royal Investments, offer our services through personal counsel with each of our clients after understanding their wealth management needs. Our approach is to enable our client's to understand their investments, have knowledge of investment products and that they make proper progress towards achieving their financial goals in life.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="col-6">
        <h5 class="dashboard_header">NEWS</h5>

    </div>
</div>

<div class="row mt-4">
    <div class="col-6">
        <h5 class="dashboard_header">WHY US</h5>

        <ul class="nav nav-pills mb-3" id="pills-tab" role="tablist">
            <li class="nav-item">
                <a class="nav-link active" id="pills-delivery-tab" data-toggle="pill" href="#pills-delivery" role="tab" aria-controls="pills-delivery" aria-selected="true">Plan</a>
            </li>
            <li class="nav-item">
                <a class="nav-link" id="pills-process-tab" data-toggle="pill" href="#pills-process" role="tab" aria-controls="pills-process" aria-selected="false">Goal</a>
            </li>
            <li class="nav-item">
                <a class="nav-link" id="pills-vision-tab" data-toggle="pill" href="#pills-vision" role="tab" aria-controls="pills-vision" aria-selected="false">Vision</a>
            </li>
        </ul>
        <div class="tab-content" id="pills-tabContent">
            <div class="tab-pane fade show active" id="pills-delivery" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="pills-delivery-tab">
                <p> In addition to our planning and execution services, we strive to establish enduring relationships with our clients, and we're committed to being there for you to witness you achieve your financial obligations and aspirations. Throughout our partnership, we'll ensure that you're kept informed, up-to-date, and in control of your wealth.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="tab-pane fade" id="pills-process" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="pills-process-tab">
                <p> Our goal is to offer straightforward, impartial, and uncomplicated professional guidance that enhances your overall well-being and generates practical solutions. We follow a client-centric, needs-based, and process-driven approach, rather than a product-oriented or sales-driven approach.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="tab-pane fade" id="pills-vision" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="pills-vision-tab">
                <p> Our vision is to offer the most suitable wealth management solutions for your complete financial wellness. Our mission is to serve as many clients as possible and make a meaningful and beneficial impact on their lives by supporting them in fulfilling their financial obligations and achieving their life goals.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>

    <div class="col-6">
