            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-header" id="headingOne">
                    <h5 class="mb-0">
                        <button class="btn dropdown-toggle collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapseOne" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="collapseOne">
                           Right People To Partner
                        </button>
                    </h5>
                </div>

                <div id="collapseOne" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="headingOne" data-parent="#accordion">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        We have rich experience in financial advisory and products distribution space. Backed with right qualifications & skills, we are the right people to engage with to ensure a smooth ride towards financial well-being.
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-header" id="headingTwo">
                    <h5 class="mb-0">
                        <button class="btn dropdown-toggle collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapseTwo" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseTwo">
